rdfs:label: rdfs:label
skos:definition: skos:definition
reg:name: reg:name

rdfs:label: en
skos:definition: en

rdfs:label: A unique token representing this element set. This will be used as the prefix identifying this URI in RDF curies or as a qname in XML
A human-readable descriptive label for the vocab. This will be displayed in lists of vocabs.
The registry code of the status (defaults to published)
A non-Registry URL that contains more information about this element set
A note about this element set
The registry ID of the owner/agent
The registry ID of the vocab admin (must be affiliated with the owner/agent)
RDA agent (person, family, corporate body) properties
is accompanied by (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item brought together with another item after being issued.
reg:name: accompaniedByItem

rdfs:label: is analysis of (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that has been examined to identify its components and their relations.
reg:name: analysisOfItem

rdfs:label: has annotator
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person who makes manuscript annotations on an item.
reg:name: annotator

rdfs:label: has autographer
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person whose manuscript signature appears on an item.
reg:name: autographer

rdfs:label: has binder
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person who binds an item.
reg:name: binder

rdfs:label: is bound with
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that has been bound within the same binding as the item being described.
reg:name: boundWith

rdfs:label: has collection registrar
skos:definition: Relates an item to a curator who lists or inventories the items in an aggregate work such as a collection of items or works.
reg:name: collectionRegistrar

rdfs:label: has collector
skos:definition: Relates an item to a curator who brings together items from various sources that are then arranged, described, and cataloged as a collection.
reg:name: collector

rdfs:label: is commentary on (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item used as the basis for a set of explanatory or critical notes.
reg:name: commentaryOnItem

rdfs:label: is contained in (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to a larger item of which a part is a discrete component.
reg:name: containedInItem

rdfs:label: is contains (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is a discrete component of a larger item.
reg:name: containsItem

rdfs:label: is critique of (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item used as the basis for a critical evaluation.
reg:name: critiqueOfItem

rdfs:label: has curator
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body conceiving, aggregating, and/or organizing an exhibition, collection, or other item.
reg:name: curator

rdfs:label: has current owner
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body currently having legal possession of an item.
reg:name: currentOwner

rdfs:label: has custodial history of item
skos:definition: Relates an item to a record of previous ownership or custodianship of an item.
reg:name: custodialHistoryOfItem

rdfs:label: has custodian
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body having legal custody of an item.
reg:name: custodian

rdfs:label: has dedicatee of item
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body to whom an item is dedicated.
reg:name: dedicateeOfItem

rdfs:label: has depositor
skos:definition: Relates an item to a current owner of an item who deposited the item into the custody of another person, family, or corporate body, while still retaining ownership.
reg:name: depositor

rdfs:label: is description of (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item described by a describing entity.
reg:name: descriptionOfItem

rdfs:label: is digital transfer of (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item transferred from one digital format to another.
reg:name: digitalTransferOfItem

rdfs:label: has donor
skos:definition: Relates an item to a former owner of an item who donated that item to another owner.
reg:name: donor

rdfs:label: is electronic reproduction of (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an analog item used as the basis for an electronic reproduction.
reg:name: electronicReproductionOfItem

rdfs:label: is equivalent item
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item embodying the same expression of a work.
reg:name: equivalentItem

rdfs:label: is evaluation of (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is examined or judged.
reg:name: evaluationOfItem

rdfs:label: is facsimile of (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item used as the basis for an exact reproduction.
reg:name: facsimileOfItem

rdfs:label: is filmed with (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is contained on the same microform with the item being described.
reg:name: filmedWithItem

rdfs:label: has former owner
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body formerly having legal possession of an item.
reg:name: formerOwner

rdfs:label: has honouree of item
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body honoured by an item, e.g., a person to whom a copy is presented.
reg:name: honoureeOfItem

rdfs:label: has identifier for the item
skos:definition: Relates an item to a character string associated with an item that serves to differentiate that item from other items.
reg:name: identifierForTheItem

rdfs:label: has illuminator
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person providing decoration to a specific item using precious metals or color, often with elaborate designs and motifs.
reg:name: illuminator

rdfs:label: has immediate source of acquisition of item
skos:definition: Relates an item to the source from which the agency directly acquired an item and the circumstances under which it was received.
reg:name: immediateSourceOfAcquisitionOfItem

rdfs:label: has inscriber
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person who has written a statement of dedication or gift on an item.
reg:name: inscriber

rdfs:label: has item-specific carrier characteristic
skos:definition: Relates an item to a characteristic that applies to the carrier or carriers of the specific item being described and is assumed not to apply to other items exemplifying the same manifestation.
reg:name: itemSpecificCarrierCharacteristic

rdfs:label: has item-specific carrier characteristic of early printed resource
skos:definition: Relates an item to a characteristic that applies to the carrier or carriers of the specific early printed item being described and is assumed not to apply to other items exemplifying the same manifestation. includes rubrication, illumination, and other hand colouring, manuscript additions, and binding.
reg:name: itemSpecificCarrierCharacteristicOfEarlyPrintedResource

rdfs:label: has manifestation exemplified
skos:definition: Relates an item to the manifestation exemplified by an item.
reg:name: manifestationExemplified

rdfs:label: has note on dimensions of item
skos:definition: Relates an item to a note providing information on the dimensions of the specific item being described that is not recorded as part of the dimensions element.
reg:name: noteOnDimensionsOfItem

rdfs:label: has note on extent of item
skos:definition: Relates an item to a note providing information on the extent of a manifestation that is not recorded as part of the extent element.
reg:name: noteOnExtentOfItem

rdfs:label: has note on manifestation or item of item
skos:definition: Relates an item to an annotation providing additional information about manifestation or item attributes.
reg:name: noteOnManifestationOrItem

rdfs:label: is on disc with (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is contained on the same disc with the item being described.
reg:name: onDiscWithItem

rdfs:label: has other person, family, or corporate body associated with an item
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body other than an owner or custodian associated with an item.
reg:name: otherPFCItem

rdfs:label: has owner
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body having legal possession of an item.
reg:name: owner

rdfs:label: is preservation facsimile of (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item used as the basis for an exact reproduction on preservation-quality media, such as acid-free permanent or archival paper.
reg:name: preservationFacsimileOfItem

rdfs:label: has related item of item
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item, represented by an identifier or a description, that is related to the resource being described (e.g., an item used as the basis for a microform reproduction).
reg:name: relatedItemOfItem

rdfs:label: is reprint of (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item that is used as the basis for a reprint with the same content as the resource being described.
reg:name: reprintOfItem

rdfs:label: is reproduction of (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item used as the basis for a reproduction.
reg:name: reproductionOfItem

rdfs:label: has restorationist
skos:definition: Relates an item to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for the set of technical, editorial, and intellectual procedures aimed at compensating for the degradation of an item by bringing it back to a state as close as possible to its original condition.
reg:name: restorationist

rdfs:label: has restrictions on access
skos:definition: Relates an item to limitations placed on access to a resource.
reg:name: restrictionsOnAccess

rdfs:label: has restrictions on use
skos:definition: Relates an item to limitations placed on uses such as reproduction, publication, exhibition, etc.
reg:name: restrictionsOnUse

rdfs:label: is review of (item)
skos:definition: Relates an item to an item used as the basis for a brief evaluation.
reg:name: reviewOfItem

rdfs:label: has seller
skos:definition: Relates an item to a former owner of an item who sold that item to another owner.
reg:name: seller
